@ 003, 060 SAY STR0006 + AllTrim(SN1->N1_DESCRIC) + STR0007 + Dtoc(cDtini) + STR0008 + Dtoc(cDtfim) FONT oBold PIXEL //"Depreciao "###" no perdo de "###" a "

@ 014, 050 TO 16 ,400 LABEL '' OF oDlg  PIXEL

ACTIVATE MSDIALOG oDlg ON INIT Atfc010Grap(oDlg, 1, aPosObj, nOpc) CENTERED

Return .T.


/*/


